  <summary>9/4/1997--Introduced.
Calls upon the President to instruct the Permanent Representative of the United States to the United Nations (UN) to act to amend the 1998-99 Regular Program Budget of the UN to eliminate funding of Kurt Waldheim's retirement allowance and to act to deny him a retirement allowance in all future UN budgets.</summary>
